Class LTLModelChecker.LTLProduct<M extends Model>

  • java.lang.Object
    • prism.Product<M>
      • prism.LTLModelChecker.LTLProduct<M>
  • Type Parameters:
    M - the underlying model type (ProbModel, NondetModel)
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    ModelTransformation<M,M>
    Enclosing class:
    LTLModelChecker

    public static class LTLModelChecker.LTLProduct<M extends Model>
extends Product<M>
    A wrapper for the product of a model (DTMC, MDP) and a deterministic omega-automaton for some linear-temporal property.
    Provides methods to obtain the product model, the acceptance condition and for translating a result in the product back to the original model.
